fallen in jargon.

00:32:01.950 --> 00:32:05.780
The three fundamental articulations
of each root have remained a sort

00:32:05.780 --> 00:32:10.000
of bone structure that has
preserved them from all softening.

00:32:10.000 --> 00:32:12.700
The Semitic script system
for its part has contributed

00:32:12.700 --> 00:32:16.370
in no small part to this
phenomenon of persistence.

00:32:16.370 --> 00:32:19.150
One cannot say that
Semites write in a manner

00:32:19.150 --> 00:32:21.520
as perfect as the Endo-Europeans.

00:32:21.520 --> 00:32:23.960
