rather than the sound.

00:32:27.690 --> 00:32:30.650
Latin and Italian, written
after the Semitic manner,

00:32:30.650 --> 00:32:33.760
would hardly differ one from
the other but one cannot deny

00:32:33.760 --> 00:32:37.060
