inconvenient to the foreigner,

00:32:37.060 --> 00:32:40.370
has not been excellent for
the conservation of roots.

00:32:40.370 --> 00:32:44.270
It has maintained the root as a
sort of perfectly pure diamond

00:32:44.270 --> 00:32:48.150
across all grammatical accidents."

00:32:48.150 --> 00:32:50.810
